 21/9/17 . Work with the school . We went with target to a rifl rang , for a shootng test . A chap beat me by a point for first place . The work is solid here near 8 hour a day . 24/9/17 . The school was move today . Went about 9 kilo past Steenvoord to billet in a farm . We are onli a few hundr yard from the frontier . Heard the 3rd Divison was about , went into Steenvoord look for Bob . He was not around . If I had got a fair go I would have been with the school a fortnight ago . 26/9/17 . Left for billet yesterday and made a new camp in a field . Carri on with the train today . There are no new stunt and I am wise to all the old one .
